      <h1>Our Pre-Prep Program</h1>
      <p>Discover our engaging Pre-Prep program designed to prepare young learners for their academic journey.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Foundation for Learning:</strong> Our Pre-Prep program builds a strong academic foundation while nurturing creativity and curiosity.</li>
        <li><strong>Qualified Teachers:</strong> Experienced educators provide individualized support to help each child thrive.</li>
        <li><strong>Interactive Learning:</strong> Hands-on activities, songs, and games make learning enjoyable and memorable.</li>
        <li><strong>Social Development:</strong> Children learn to collaborate, share, and build friendships in a supportive environment.</li>
        <li><strong>Character Building:</strong> Christian values are integrated to instill kindness, respect, and honesty.</li>
      </ul>
